skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gastroenterology clinical focus
des: Are you a gastroenterology trainee or practicing physician? Challenge yourself and ask Alexa to quiz you on different gastroenterology topics using content from the book "Gastroenterology Clinical Focus" by Emad Qayed, MD, MPH. Questions are brief, with 3-4 answer choices, and a brief answer explanation. Provide the answer and try to achieve a high score. One to four players can play. Good luck!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
